{"tid":287450,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"潮 聯 小 巴 成 撚 日 唔 停 車 熄 匙 ， 好 撚 嬲","createTime":"2017-06-17T12:09:32.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-18T16:32:34.000Z","uid":42250,"like":21,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"47e11d26b87f01dfbc699d78fa9fcd572e3be413","tid":287450,"uid":42250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T12:09:32.000Z","msg":"idlingenq@epd.gov.hk<br />\n<br />\n敬啟者： <br />\n<br />\n本人已欲告發有大量小巴懷疑違反《汽車引擎空轉(定額罰款)條例》，在小巴站內停定小巴時讓內燃引擎於任何連續的60分鐘時段內合計運作超過3分鐘(&quot;停車熄匙規定&quot;)。 <br />\n<br />\n地點：通菜街與亞皆老街交界小巴站 <br />\n<br />\n請貴組跟進以上投訴並以電郵回覆跟進情況。謝謝！ <br />\n<br />\n此致 <br />\n環境保護署 流動污染源組 <br />\n<br />\n投訴人 <br />\n陳先生"},{"pid":"180890b83840dbe499639189a3315f230faf3d0f","tid":287450,"uid":30807,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T12:10:03.000Z","msg":"g持"},{"pid":"7d0b570f6b84e39304064f4daa53302efd63c918","tid":287450,"uid":52132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T12:11:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b7ff6431b51329a11dfb744618978857c31def95","tid":287450,"uid":42250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T12:15:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3daac0f5843408da83f968bf44cdccfab2c8a4d8","tid":287450,"uid":4493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T12:56:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b81b570ef136d3f36529abdaca0ea30310ece40","tid":287450,"uid":99461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T13:12:09.000Z","msg":"."},{"pid":"d276ac00bdf38843180d47e1ecada1fba803cf02","tid":287450,"uid":9838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T13:13:15.000Z","msg":"send"},{"pid":"74e8056f3d503f0f3f898bf00fbeb1bf24834757","tid":287450,"uid":32723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T13:14:42.000Z","msg":"仆街, 好多人坐架個D 小巴<br />\n